Maxima closed the distance upon her flight return to the Pred base. However, 
in the meantime, she rendezvoused with Blackstorm as she detected the femme 
nearby & changed course just enough to intercept. Noticing also a couple others 
with her.

Opening a com to Blackstorm, >"Blackstorm this is Maxima. Comrades or 
prisoners?"< she was very too the point & dry about the question. 

--part1_bb.31bcd3da.2c01acb9_boundary
